OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781858896
OL,3,CUK drops 'do not travel' warning for
OL,4,CUAE and other Gulf nations
OL,6,FThe Foreign Office has lifted its "do
OL,7,Fnot travel" warning for a host of Gulf
OL,8,Fnations, including the UAE, after the
OL,9,FUS and Iran signed a deal aimed at
OL,10,Fending the war.
OL,12,FSince the outbreak of the war at the
OL,13,Fend of February, the UK has advised
OL,14,Fagainst travelling to a host of Middle
OL,15,FEastern nations.
OL,17,FBut on Thursday, it lifted the warning
OL,18,Ffor the UAE, as well as Kuwait,
OL,19,FBahrain, Oman and Qatar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
