CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781858896
OL,3,CUK drops 'do not travel' warning for
OL,4,CUAE and other Gulf nations
OL,6,FThey are still in place for Saudi
OL,7,FArabia, Iraq, Jordan, Israel, Iran,
OL,8,FSyria, Lebanon and Yemen, as well as
OL,9,Fpart of Turkey and Egypt.
OL,11,FSome of these warnings predate the US-
OL,12,FIsrael war with Iran.
OL,14,FFor the nations where the Foreign
OL,15,FOffice has dropped its warning, it
OL,16,Fstill highlights "the situation
OL,17,Fremains unpredictable, and attacks
OL,18,Fcould resume at short notice."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
