FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781858896
OL,3,CUK drops 'do not travel' warning for
OL,4,CUAE and other Gulf nations
OL,6,FIt says if hostilities resume, British
OL,7,Fnationals should inform the Foreign
OL,8,FOffice of their presence in the
OL,9,Fcountry, stay away from security or
OL,10,Fmilitary facilities, keep up to date
OL,11,Fwith departure plans and follow the
OL,12,Fadvice of local authorities.
OL,14,FIt also warns that Iran has previously
OL,15,Fsaid it would target organisations or
OL,16,Fbusinesses connected to the US or
OL,17,FIsrael in the region and said these
OL,18,Fcould be targeted again if hostilities
OL,19,Fresume.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781858896
OL,3,CUK drops 'do not travel' warning for
OL,4,CUAE and other Gulf nations
OL,6,FThousands of Brits were left stranded
OL,7,Fin the Middle East when the conflict
OL,8,Fbroke out, and many airlines have
OL,9,Fstill not returned to the region.
OL,11,FThe war has had a significant impact
OL,12,Fon the region's economy, particularly
OL,13,Fin the cities of Dubai, Abu Dhabi, and
OL,14,FDoha.
OL,16,FOver 1.4 million Brits visited Dubai
OL,17,Flast year, including via its major
OL,18,Finternational airport, which has
OL,19,Fbecome a global hub for transfers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781858896
OL,3,CUK drops 'do not travel' warning for
OL,4,CUAE and other Gulf nations
OL,6,FThe lifting of the 'do not travel'
OL,7,Fadvice means most travel insurance in
OL,8,Fthe impacted nations will now be valid.
OL,10,FBut most travel insurance policies do
OL,11,Fnot protect their customers against
OL,12,Facts of war, so travellers will still
OL,13,Fneed to weigh up the risks.
OL,15,FFlights to the region have also not
OL,16,Freturned to how they were previously,
OL,17,Fwith many carriers saying they will
OL,18,Fnot fly to the region for many months.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
