OL,3,CUK drops 'do not travel' warning for
OL,4,CUAE and other Gulf nations
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe only major carrier still flying
OL,12,Ffrom the UK to the region is Emirates,
OL,13,Fwhich is owned by the UAE.
OL,15,FIran and the US signed a deal on
OL,16,FThursday, bringing the war to an end
OL,17,Fearlier this week. A 60-day period is
OL,18,Fnow underway, during which the two
OL,19,Fsides will work out a plan to remove
OL,20,FIran's nuclear material.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781858896
OL,3,CUK drops 'do not travel' warning for
OL,4,CUAE and other Gulf nations
OL,6,FThe US said the deal would mean the
OL,7,Freopening of the Strait of Hormuz, the
OL,8,Fcritical shipping lane through which
OL,9,Fmost of the region's oil travels.
OL,11,FOn Thursday, US Vice President JD
OL,12,FVance said 12.5 million barrels of oil
OL,13,Fpassed through the Strait of Hormuz on
OL,14,FWednesday night, after the deal was
OL,15,Fsigned.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781858896
OL,3,CUK drops 'do not travel' warning for
OL,4,CUAE and other Gulf nations
OL,6,FBut many of the details still need to
OL,7,Fbe worked out, and US War Secretary
OL,8,FPete Hegseth threatened on Thursday
OL,9,Fthat the US was prepared to resume
OL,10,Fmilitary action if Tehran fails to
OL,11,Fuphold the latest peace agreement
OL,12,Fbetween the two countries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
